    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>妄想症</strong>是一款第一人称心理恐怖步行模拟器，专注于营造紧张氛围。游戏时长大约30-45分钟。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个对你的每一个动作都做出反应的郊区房屋。观看怀旧风格的恐怖电视广播。解决轻度谜题，例如解锁门并进入新区域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏是一个以氛围和紧张感为核心的线性体验。它在叙事或机制上并不复杂——更像是一场令人毛骨悚然的游乐设施。如果你正在寻找这种体验，那么这里就是你的归属。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293250/extras/6023d245906e5be74827841ea322c8d9.poster.avif?t=1740978160\" width=616 height=462 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293250/extras/6023d245906e5be74827841ea322c8d9.webm?t=1740978160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293250/extras/6023d245906e5be74827841ea322c8d9.mp4?t=1740978160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p>",
